ores detalhes das mudanas.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Como ajudar</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ajude a traduo em Portugus!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp/dev/pt-br/default\">Ajude-nos a traduzir o WordPress para o portugus!</a>&nbsp;O lanamento dessa verso tambm significa que&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/polyglots/handbook/glossary/#hard-freeze\">novas strings para traduo</a>&nbsp;da verso 5.4 sero evitadas.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><strong>Se acha que encontrou um erro</strong>, voc pode public-lo na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/forum/alphabeta\">rea Alpha/Beta</a>&nbsp;nos fruns de suporte (em ingls). Ns vamos adorar ouvir voc! Se voc se sente confortvel para escrever um relatrio de como reproduzir o erro,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/reports/\">envie para o Trac do WordPress</a>, onde tambm  possvel encontrar uma&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/tickets/major\">lista de erros conhecidos</a>.</em></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress 5.4 RC3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2020/03/17/wordpress-5-4-rc3/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 17 Mar 2020 22:56:45 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lanamentos\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\